WEBVTT

00:08:28.477 --> 00:08:31.683
I had to eat a big piece
of humble pie to admit

00:08:32.469 --> 00:08:34.874
that I had made a mistake

00:08:34.898 --> 00:08:37.739
and inadvertently become
a part of the problem.

00:08:38.814 --> 00:08:41.142
I had been an orphanage tourist,

00:08:41.166 --> 00:08:43.027
a voluntourist.

00:08:43.051 --> 00:08:48.034
I then set up my own orphanage
and facilitated orphanage tourism

00:08:48.058 --> 00:08:50.707
in order to generate funds
for my orphanage,

00:08:51.461 --> 00:08:53.065
before I knew better.

00:08:54.375 --> 00:08:56.383
What I came to learn

00:08:56.407 --> 00:08:59.817
is that no matter how good
my orphanage was,

00:08:59.841 --> 00:09:04.496
it was never going to give those kids
what they really needed: